claim.claim-text:
1. A liquid detergent composition comprising:
a) from about 0.01% to about 1.5% by weight of the composition of an alkoxylated polyethyleneimine polymer comprising
(1) a polyethyleneimine backbone wherein the polyethyleneimine backbone has a weight average molecular weight from about 400 g/mol to about 6000 g/mol;
(2) a polyoxyethylene chain having an average of from about 1 to about 30 ethylene oxide units per unit of NH on the polyethyleneimine backbone;
(3) a quaternization permanent degree between about 75% and about 100%; and

b) from about 0.5% to about 40% by weight of a surfactant selected from the group consisting of nonionic, anionic, amphoteric, zwitterionic, cationic, or a mixture thereof.
